      <title>科特迪瓦可可贸易集团称出口商为可可豆支付过高的价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/ivory-coast-cocoa-trade-group-says-exporters-overpay-for-beans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，科特迪瓦贸易商团体成员抱怨称，世界上一些主要可可种植国的可可豆出口商为确保其加工厂的供应而支付了过高的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/ivory-coast-cocoa-trade-group-says-exporters-overpay-for-beans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 13:57:10 GMT</pubDate>
