    <item>
      <title>选举结果引发新一轮骚乱 莫桑比克局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/mozambique-on-edge-after-election-results-ignite-fresh-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克当局于周四晚宣布执政党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，反对派认为选举存在舞弊行为，随后首都爆发骚乱，国内局势高度紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/mozambique-on-edge-after-election-results-ignite-fresh-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 13:12:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
