      <title>巴克莱银行赢得法庭裁决，削减英国投资者暗池交易诉讼的价值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/barclays-wins-court-cut-in-value-of-uk-investor-dark-pool-trading-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法官驳回一系列指控后，巴克莱银行成功将投资者就其暗池交易系统的指控在伦敦提起的诉讼金额削减了一半以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/barclays-wins-court-cut-in-value-of-uk-investor-dark-pool-trading-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 12:19:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通货膨胀持续，俄罗斯将基准利率上调至创纪录的 21%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/russia-raises-key-rate-to-record-21-as-inflation-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯央行将基准利率上调至历史新高，超过了总统普京下令入侵乌克兰后设定的利率水平，并暗示由于政策制定者努力应对持续的通胀，未来可能进一步收紧政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/russia-raises-key-rate-to-record-21-as-inflation-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cepsa 或将效仿 Repsol 并限制绿色氢能投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/spain-s-cepsa-to-pull-spending-on-green-hydrogen-if-tax-approved</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府正在考虑税收改革，因此西班牙炼油商 Cepsa 可能会效仿其竞争对手 Repsol，限制国内绿色氢能投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/spain-s-cepsa-to-pull-spending-on-green-hydrogen-if-tax-approved</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 07:56:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
